channel.title: Iamaminer1......... PSYCHIC?!?!
channel.description:
A while back iamaminer1 predicted that a new forum rule was coming on The-Unamed i'm leaving for the holidays thread [url=http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,27197.msg311921.html#msg311921]here[/url] he said that he thought a new forum specific rule was coming. He was correct. Shortly after, one of the moderators declared that no more leaving threads were allowed in this forum. Here is a quote from iamaminer1's statement:
[quote="iamaminer1, post:4, topic:18190"]lol, i think a new forum rule is coming.............[/quote]
Obviously he's psychic.
DISCUSS IT [url=http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,37169.msg447714.html#msg447714]HERE[/url]!
O, and we must always remember iamaminer1's famous catchphrase:
I DONT THINK YOU FUKIN GET IT, I THINK I DELETED THE FUKIN INTERNET EXPLOER!1111!!!!!111111!!!
Iamaminer brought us laughter, the sweetest laughter of them all. The joy of seeing an idiot struggle with a computer.
